snippet.title: Earth From Another Sun - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Earth From Another Sun is an ambitious MMOFPS set in an open galaxy!
Explore the galaxy, establish and grow your empire, build your trade network, fight alongside the armies you command, and conquer the galaxy! 

Access the Alpha on https://earthfromanothersun.com

Join us:
https://discord.gg/EFAS
https://www.facebook.com/MultiverseVR
https://twitter.com/PlayEFAS
